        "TileImage": "$($repository 233503c3-d3bd-4900-b501-90d4c95b03d4).Image",
        "Description": "Good afternoon 47,\r\rAn ICA employee has a close relationship with our client, the owner of a bakery in Whittleton Creek. Recently, the emergence of a rival business in the area is winning the loyalty of the client&apos;s longstanding customers and draining his profits.\r\rTheir award-winning cake recipes are only known to the businesses&apos; close-knit group of employees; therefore, the entire staff team must be eliminated.\r\rThe client has requested a short, sharp ending for the targets.\r\rGood luck 47.",
